title: Ruean Chadanang
overview: The story follows three sisters from a Thai dancing house nicknamed "Tre Chada" meaning Trio Tiara. The eldest, Chadaohorn, is the most beautiful woman one could lay eyes on, unmatched by anybody. The middle, Chadaploy, has an air of free-spiritedness and self-confidence. Finally, the youngest, Chadapetch, is just as mean as she is pretty, and loves to compete with people.
